high_descs: Walk over to the small red bin on the ground to your right.
Pick up the purple spray bottle out of the red bin.
Turn around and walk towards the shower, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Put the purple spray bottle on the counter in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Move a purple spray bottle to the counter.

high_descs: Move to the red trash bin against the wall of the bathroom
Pick up the purple bottle inside of the trash bin
Carry the purple bottle over to the middle of the two sinks
Place the purple bottle on top of the counter between the two sinks
anns.task_desc: Move the spray bottle to the counter top

high_descs: Turn right and head to the red trash can across the room
Pick up the spray bottle that is inside the trash can
Turn around and head forward then make a right and walk to the counter top between the two sinks
Place the spray bottle on the counter top between the two sinks
anns.task_desc: Place a spray bottle on a counter top
